name: 90s anime vibes LoRA (style)
description:
This is a lora I meant to do for a while. It captures the essence of the 90s anime vibe. It also have a touch of vaporwave into it making it more of a retro 90s aesthetic then 100% anime.

90s vibes, 1990s \(style\) add to your prompt for more effect, but you really don't need them.

Best keep under 0.75 weight, 0.5 being the sweet spot.

Best for SFW but can also do NSFW

Installation of the LORA:

Copy the Axsens.safetensors file into the \stable-diffusion-webui\models\lora folder.
